{
  "stem": "14613.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You could see sick people on the streets, dying people on the streets.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] You have-- there was not enough people to bury the dead people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So you could see them, with a horse and buggy, being sent out from ghetto for-- for burial.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you know, it's still an amazing thing that, in spite of all of this, at least my experience where I went, when I worked in the-- in the ghetto, which was called the [NON-ENGLISH] resort, which means-- how to translate it-- where we were sewing some leather knapsacks for the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was mostly-- this particular resort was mostly [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was mostly for young people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Somehow, coincidence, we were a lot of young people working in this resort.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we have understood that, if we're going to work so hard, like many other resorts, just to get another piece of bread-- we're going to use too much energy.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And therefore, and this is really-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in ghetto, there was a creation of a certain, call it a communist movement.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And some of the leaders in the communist movement-- some of them were very good friends of mine, that we went to school together-- they-- they organized, and in particular, our resort was excellent to it, that we did what we would call here in, the United States, like slow-down strikes.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "When the management wanted us to do 10 pieces a day, we would do only 2.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And-- and we realized that the management would be afraid to do anything to us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because if they openly would say that, hey, you've got a slow-down strike, they would be punished by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
